\par\par \b \uc2 Revising the 2005  \highlight22\uc2 budget \highlight\b0\par\par\uc2 729 \uc2 words\par \uc2 9 June 2005\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 6\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2005 The Jakarta Post   \par \par \uc2 The government and the \b \highlight22\uc2 Budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  Committee of the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  have agreed on the most significant changes needed to the 2005 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , paving the way for the approval of a revised \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 , which has been made necessary by much-higher-than-anticipated oil prices and the devastating earthquake and tsunami in Aceh last December.   \par \par \uc2 Speedy enactment of the long-awaited \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  revisions is crucial, especially for the disbursement of funds for poverty alleviation, special assistance funds for poor families as compensation for the inflationary impact of the March fuel-price increases, and money for the reconstruction of Aceh province.   \par \par \uc2 Changes in major \b \highlight22\uc2 expenditure\b0 \highlight\uc2  items for the whole year are based on new key assumptions: average international oil price of US$45/barrel (up from previous estimate of $24), \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth of 6 percent (5.5 percent), average rupiah exchange rate of Rp 9,300 (Rp 8,600), interest rate of 8 percent (6.5 percent), and inflation at 8 percent ( 5.5 percent).   \par \par \uc2 The market will be more comfortable with the new assumptions as they are more realistic, meaning that the total amount of money the government will spend will be closely aligned to what is affordable over the current year.   \par \par \uc2 Predictability is important for efficient and effective implementation of policies and programs because the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  sector will perform better where there is stability in macro and strategic \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and funding for existing policies.   \par \par \uc2 The wild volatility of the rupiah exchange rate, which reached as high as 6.22 percent in May, as against a fluctuation of only about 3.5 percent in April, can partly be blamed on the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  caused by the unrealistic \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  estimates.   \par \par \uc2 The amendments will increase total government \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  to more than Rp 510 trillion ($54.8 billion), compared to Rp 395 trillion as originally envisaged. Encouraging, though, is the fact that the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  will be maintained at the original estimate, or at 0.8 percent of gross domestic product.   \par \par \uc2 This will be made possible because the government will cover the additional \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  by increasing the total nominal amount of the bonds to be issued this year to Rp 47.1 trillion from Rp 43 trillion as previously planned. More than Rp 24 trillion in savings on foreign debt servicing as a result of the recent decision by the Paris Club of sovereign creditors to reschedule Indonesian debt service payments due this year will also help curb the \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 The revision of the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  has been imperative since early this year due mainly to persistently high oil prices and the need for huge sums of money to be spent on the reconstruction of Aceh after the earthquake and tsunami.   \par \par \uc2 The government initially assumed that the average oil price would be $24/barrel for the whole year. This was revised upward to $35 when the government raised domestic fuel prices by an average 29 percent in March.   \par \par \uc2 However, most analysts estimate the average oil price for the whole year will most likely hover at $50. During the first five months alone, the oil price averaged $50.75 and is predicted to remain at about the same level even during the summer due to the strong demand from China, currently the world's second largest consumer, and insecurity of supply from the Middle East.   \par \par \uc2 This single change alone has created a chain of consequences that require the revision of the estimates for state receipts, the rupiah exchange rate, \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2 , and fuel \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and social-safety net \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  programs. These are the changes that will be accommodated in the minibudget expected to be approved within the next few days.   \par \par \uc2 For example, based on the new oil price assumption ($45), the government and the House \b \highlight22\uc2 Budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  Committee have agreed to revise upward the fuel \b \highlight22\uc2 subsidy\b0 \highlight\uc2  appropriation to Rp 76.5 trillion.   \par \par \uc2 But as the high oil prices are causing stronger inflationary pressures in the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , the rupiah is also experiencing downward pressure, forcing the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  to tighten its money \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  by upping \b \highlight22\uc2 interest rates\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 The government and the House need to complete the deliberations on the revision of the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  as quickly as possible as the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  represents a communications system that conveys signals about behavior, prices, priorities and commitments. A more realistic \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  will reduce \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  about \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  sector \b \highlight22\uc2 expenditure\b0 \highlight\uc2  and structural imbalances between expectations and resources.   \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020050609e1690000n\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
